## 5. HOME TAB

### HomeView layout
- Header: "Hi, {firstName}" greeting (first name only from profile.fullName)
- **Next booking card**: shows only if upcoming confirmed booking exists, with same-day follow-on count indicator (hidden when 0 follow-ons)
- **"Games Near You" carousel**: scrollable horizontal card list
  - Data: `allUpcomingGames` filtered to: `status == "upcoming"`, next 7 days, within 75 km of effective user location, NOT already booked (confirmed/waitlisted only)
  - Games whose club has no coordinates resolved yet: INCLUDED (not silently dropped)
  - Sorted: soonest first, then nearest first
- **"More games" CTA**: opens `NearbyGamesView` (full list) as sheet
- **Suburb search**: allows geocoding a suburb name via `PlaceSearchService` to use as fake GPS origin for distance sorting
- **Pickleball news section**: RSS feed (The Dink), up to 5 articles, opens in `SafariView` (Chrome Custom Tabs equivalent) ‚Äî **OUT OF SCOPE for Android v1**

### Nearby games filter logic
- Games hidden from carousel if `booking.state` is `.confirmed` or `.waitlisted` for that game
- Cancelled and failed-payment bookings do NOT hide the game
- Distance filter: 75 km radius when location available; all games when no location
- Location source priority: `locationManager.userLocation` ‚Üí `suburbSearchLocation` (geocoded)
- Log line emitted: `[HomeFilter] DROP 'title' status=X days=Y booked=Z inWindow=W` (debug only, not for Android)

### NearbyDiscoveryView (map + bottom panel)
- Presented as `.sheet` over HomeView
- Map: `Map` with game pins colored by spot availability
- Bottom panel: custom draggable panel ‚Äî three states: `.minimized` (72dp), `.collapsed` (320dp), `.expanded` (82% screen height)
- Pin tap ‚Üí scrolls list panel to that game, highlights card
- Card tap ‚Üí centers map on pin AND centers scroll
- Card body tap ‚Üí opens `GameDetailView` (full screen, not sheet in this context)
- Filters:
  - Distance: Any / 5 km / 10 km / 25 km
  - Skill: nil (any) or specific skill level string
  - Day: Any / Today / This Week
- Game sort: available-today ‚Üí available-soon ‚Üí full games last; capped at 50 games

