## 8. BOOKINGS LIST VIEW

### Grouping logic
- Groups: `thisWeek`, `nextTwoWeeks`, `laterThisMonth`, `past`
- `thisWeek`: same ISO week (Calendar.current weekOfYear) as now
- `nextTwoWeeks`: after this week, within 14 days from now
- `laterThisMonth`: beyond 14 days
- `past`: before now
- Default expanded groups on launch: `thisWeek`, `nextTwoWeeks`, `laterThisMonth`
- Past group: collapsed by default; toggled via "Show Past Bookings" button

### Visibility rules
- **Upcoming sections**: cancelled bookings HIDDEN (would look like game cancellations)
- **Past section**: only `confirmed` bookings shown (confirmed at game time = assumed attendance)
- Past section only appears when "Show Past Bookings" toggle is on

### "Next booking" accent
- The earliest confirmed upcoming booking gets a subtle lime accent (regardless of which section bucket it's in)
- `nextBookingID` computed from `appState.bookings` filtered to confirmed + future

### Credit pills
- Shown below bookings list: one pill per club with positive balance
- Loaded in `.task` via `withTaskGroup` concurrently for all club IDs in user's bookings
- On `lastCancellationCredit` change: immediately refresh that club's balance (no pull-to-refresh needed)

### History toggle button
- Shows: clock icon + "Show Past Bookings" when off / "Showing Past + Future" when on
- Also shows "Upcoming Only" chip when off
- Past group auto-expanded (spring animation) when toggle turns on

### Pull-to-refresh
- Calls `appState.refreshBookings()`

### Booking card tap
- Sets `selectedGame` ‚Üí `navigationDestination(item:)` push to `GameDetailView`

