## 9. NOTIFICATIONS VIEW

### Structure
- Uses its OWN inner `NavigationStack` (not the tab's outer one)
- Title: "Notifications" (large, rounded, no navigation bar ‚Äî `.toolbar(.hidden, for: .navigationBar)`)
- Refresh: pull-to-refresh calls `appState.refreshNotifications()`

### Action row (shown when notifications exist)
- Unread count label: "X unread" (hidden if 0)
- "Mark all read" button (shown only if unread > 0)
- "Clear" button (trash icon, errorRed tint) ‚Üí shows `.alert` confirmation ‚Üí calls `appState.clearAllNotifications()`

### Notification row visual
- `iconBadge`: 42√ó42 circle, color from `notification.type.accentColorName`, SF Symbol icon
- Read indicator: 8√ó8 teal circle (top-right) ‚Äî shown when `!notification.read`
- Chevron: shown when `hasDestination == true`
- Unread border: 1.5pt stroke with accentColor.opacity(0.35)
- Read border: 1pt `Brand.softOutline`
- Relative timestamp: `.formatted(.relative(presentation: .named))` (e.g. "2 hours ago")

### Notification tap routing
```
.game(id):
  ‚Üí search gamesByClubID.values + bookings cache
  ‚Üí if found: set selectedGame (sheet over NotificationsView)
  ‚Üí if NOT found: returns nil, hasDestination = false, no navigation (unlike MainTabView which fetches from DB)
  NOTE: game notifications where the game is not in memory show no chevron and are NOT tappable

.club(id):
  ‚Üí find in appState.clubs
  ‚Üí set selectedClub ‚Üí navigationDestination push inline (back returns to Notifications)

.review(gameID):
  ‚Üí ALWAYS tappable (hasDestination always true for review type)
  ‚Üí extracts game title from notification.title: strips "How was " prefix and "?" suffix
  ‚Üí fallback title: "Your Session"
  ‚Üí set pendingReview ‚Üí ReviewGameSheet as sheet
```

### Review sheet trigger
- `ReviewGameSheet(gameID: review.id, gameTitle: review.gameTitle)` ‚Äî does NOT pass a Game object
- Club resolved inside ReviewGameSheet via `appState.clubForGame(gameID:)` (memory ‚Üí DB fallback)
- After submit, "View [Club Name]" button available: calls `onViewClub` closure ‚Üí dismiss sheet + open club via selectedClub

### Notification type ‚Üí icon + color mapping
See `AppNotification.NotificationType` in Models.swift. Key mappings:
- `booking_confirmed` ‚Üí `checkmark.seal.fill` / emeraldAction
- `game_cancelled` ‚Üí `xmark.circle.fill` / errorRed
- `waitlist_promoted` ‚Üí `arrow.up.circle.fill` / pineTeal
- `club_announcement` ‚Üí `megaphone.fill` / spicyOrange
- `club_chat_mention` ‚Üí `at.circle.fill` / slateBlue
- `game_review_request` ‚Üí `star.bubble.fill` / pineTeal
- `new_game` ‚Üí `plus.circle.fill` / emeraldAction
- `membership_approved` ‚Üí `person.badge.checkmark.fill` / emeraldAction
- `membership_rejected` ‚Üí `person.badge.minus.fill` / errorRed

