- Sorted alphabetically by club name
- One row per club: club name + formatted balance
- Loaded in `.task` via `withTaskGroup` for all booking club IDs

### Refresh (pull-to-refresh)
- `refreshProfile()` + `refreshBookings(silent: true)` + `refreshMemberships()` + concurrent credit refresh for all booking club IDs

### Edit Profile button ‚Üí `EditProfileSheet` (navigation hub)
Sections inside the hub sheet:
1. Personal Info ‚Üí `ProfilePersonalInfoView` (full name, date of birth)
2. Contact ‚Üí `ProfileContactView` (email read-only, phone editable)
3. DUPR ‚Üí `ProfileDUPRView` (DUPR ID + doubles + singles ratings)
