- Delete Account (destructive alert ‚Äî not yet implemented server-side)

### ProfileDUPRView storage split
- DUPR ID: UserDefaults only (no Supabase column); key: `bookadink.profile.duprIDByUserID`
- Doubles rating: UserDefaults + synced to `profiles.dupr_rating` via PATCH
- Singles rating: UserDefaults only (`@AppStorage("duprSinglesRating")`) ‚Äî NO Supabase column
- Rating validation: 1.0‚Äì8.0 enforced client-side
- DUPR history: UserDefaults (`bookadink.profile.duprHistoryByUserID`); NOT synced to Supabase in v1

### ProfileNotificationsView (notification preferences)
- Reads iOS push authorization status via `UNUserNotificationCenter`
- Shows "Open iOS Settings" button if `pushStatus != .authorized`
- Push toggles only shown when `pushStatus == .authorized`
- Push types: booking confirmations, new games, waitlist updates, member chat/posts
- Email types: booking confirmations, new games, waitlist updates
- Footer: "Club announcements always push through regardless of these settings"
- Saved to Supabase via `appState.saveNotificationPreferences()` on `onChange(of: prefs)`

### Pinned clubs
- `pinnedClubIDs: [UUID]` stored in UserDefaults (`bookadink.home.pinnedClubIDs`)
- Used to sort Home tab club section

