## 15. ROLE-BASED BEHAVIOUR MATRIX

| Surface | Player (non-member) | Approved Member | Club Admin / Owner |
|---|---|---|---|
| Club detail toolbar | No admin button | No admin button | Grid icon (opens Dashboard fullScreenCover) |
| Join/Leave CTA | "Request to Join" / "Leave" visible | "Leave Club" (if removable) | Hidden (owner can't leave) |
| Games tab ‚Äî scheduled games | Hidden | Hidden | Shown (dimmed, orange "Not visible" banner) |
| Attendee list on GameDetailView | Locked icon + count only | Full list with initials | Full list + payment badges |
| Payment badge (Card/Comp/Unpaid) | Hidden | Hidden | Shown in attendee list |
| Chat composer | Cannot post (canPost = false) | Can post; no announcement toggle | Can post; announcement toggle visible |
| Book CTA | Disabled if not member | Enabled per booking rules | Enabled (can also admin-add others) |
| Cancel booking | Own bookings only | Own bookings only | Can cancel any attendee's booking |
| Admin add player | N/A | N/A | "Add Player" section in GameDetailView |
| Attendance check-in | N/A | N/A | Tappable attendance controls in GameDetailView |
| Club Dashboard (fullScreenCover) | Not accessible | Not accessible | Opened via grid toolbar button |

