| Gap | Backend Change Required |
|---|---|
| FCM push notifications | Add `fcm_token` column to `profiles`; update 5+ Edge Functions to send to FCM |

### Android equivalents (platform mapping)
| iOS | Android |
|---|---|
| APNs token ‚Üí `profiles.apns_token` | FCM token ‚Üí `profiles.fcm_token` |
| `UNUserNotificationCenter` | `NotificationManager` / `FirebaseMessagingService` |
| `SafariView` (SFSafariViewController) | Chrome Custom Tabs |
