| Local push reminder | NOT required for v1 |
| UserDefaults | DataStore Preferences |
| `@AppStorage` | DataStore Preferences |
| `PhotosPickerItem` (image upload) | NOT required for v1 |
| `StripePaymentSheet` | `PaymentSheet` (Stripe Android SDK) |
| Apple Pay | Google Pay via `GooglePayConfig(countryCode="AU", currencyCode="aud")` |
| `CLLocationManager` | `FusedLocationProviderClient` |
| `fullScreenCover` | `Dialog` (full-screen) or new Activity |
| `NavigationStack` + `navigationDestination(item:)` | Navigation Compose `NavHost` + `navigate()` |
| `LazyVStack` / `LazyHStack` | `LazyColumn` / `LazyRow` |
| `ScrollView { }` | `Column` inside `Scaffold` or `LazyColumn` |

### State management equivalences
| iOS | Android |
|---|---|
| `@StateObject AppState` | `@Singleton AppStateHolder` (Hilt) |
| `@Published var X` | `StateFlow<X>` |
| `@State private var X` (screen-scoped) | `var X by remember { mutableStateOf(...) }` |
| `@State private var commentDraft` (card-scoped) | `var draft by remember { mutableStateOf("") }` in Card Composable |
| `@EnvironmentObject appState` | `@HiltViewModel` + `collectAsState()` |

