## 19. VIOLATION IMPACT

| Violation | Impact |
|---|---|
| Lifting comment draft to ViewModel/feed | Full card list recomposition on every keystroke ‚Äî keyboard lag |
| Global credit balance instead of club-scoped Map | Multi-club users show wrong credit balance; credits applied to wrong club |
| Reading injected game param instead of currentGame | Credit balance check against stale fee; user sees wrong net price |
| Calling confirmPendingBooking without clubID | Credit deduction silently skipped |
| Not lowercasing UUIDs in PostgREST filters | 0 rows returned silently ‚Äî bookings, credits, attendees all appear empty |
| Sending `tournament` as skill_level | PostgreSQL enum error 22P02 ‚Äî game creation or profile save fails |
| Presenting fullScreenCover on isAuthenticating | Overlays main tab view during token refresh ‚Äî user sees loading screen mid-session |
| Loading all club tab data on ClubDetailView open | Performance freeze; violates "load on tab change only" rule |
| Using use_credits or issue_cancellation_credit via PostgREST | PGRST202 ‚Äî function not found; credit operations silently fail |
| Not handling notification.game not in memory | Game notifications become untappable when game not cached |
